lead_paragraph: Todd Frazier hit a tiebreaking grand slam in the 12th inning for his second homer of the game, powering the Chicago White Sox to an 8-4 victory over the Texas Rangers on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Frazier's Slam in 12th Leads White Sox Past Rangers 8-4
